%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^RED%^Evil Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Drawing fully upon the forces of pure evil, this domain blesses those of like hearts while harming most those who are directly opposite in beliefs. However, the spells involved will still affect those even of the same alignment. Most spells will only work for a priest of evil alignment.

The evil domain contains the following spells:

Touch of sickening, Align Weapon, Contagion*, Fear, Slay living, Create Undead, Blasphemy, Unholy aura, Animus Blast

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow, The Faceless One, Nilith

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
